gw.plugin.purge

Interface WorksheetPurgePlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface WorksheetPurgePlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    Interface for controlling worksheet purge. Purging worksheets is performed by the WorksheetPurgeWorkQueue.

    • Method Detail

      • buildWorksheetCandidatesQuery

        void buildWorksheetCandidatesQuery(IQueryBuilder<WorksheetContainer> query,
                                   java.util.Date purgeDate)
        Add restrictions to the given query so that only worksheet containers eligible for purging are picked up.
        Parameters:
        query - Query which selects WorksheetContainers.
        purgeDate - Date on which the purge will be performed (generally today)

      • canPurgeWorksheetContainer

        boolean canPurgeWorksheetContainer(java.util.Date purgeDate,
                                   WorksheetContainer worksheetContainer)
        Final check to make sure that a worksheet container is really able to be purged.
        Parameters:
        purgeDate - Date on which the purge will be performed (generally today)
        worksheetContainer - The worksheet container
        Returns:
        true iff worksheetContainer can be purged

      • getAgeThreshold

        int getAgeThreshold()
        Returns:
        the age that a worksheet container must be before it is eligible to be purged (in days).
